Paper: hep-th/9707155

Date: 1997-07-17

Title: Factorization of Multiparticle Scattering in the Heisenberg Spin Chain

Authors: Anastasia Doikou, Luca Mezincescu and Rafael I. Nepomechie

Comments: 9 pages, LaTeX, no figures

SystemsJournal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A12 (1997) 2591-2598

We give an explicit proof within the framework of the Bethe Ansatz/stringhypothesis of the factorization of multiparticle scattering in theantiferromagnetic spin-1/2 Heisenberg spin chain, for the case of 3 particles.